---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout seo={{ title: "About", description: "About HealthPulse — India's healthcare publishing platform" }}>
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">About HealthPulse</h1>

		<div class="prose prose-lg prose-healthcare max-w-none">
			<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
				HealthPulse is India's healthcare publishing platform — delivering expert insights on hospital management, clinical excellence, health technology, and patient education.
			</p>

			<h2>Our Mission</h2>
			<p>
				We believe better-informed healthcare professionals build better hospitals. And better-informed patients make better health decisions. HealthPulse bridges the gap between medical expertise and actionable knowledge.
			</p>

			<h2>Who We Write For</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Hospital Leaders</strong> — CEOs, CMOs, CFOs, and board members who shape healthcare strategy</li>
				<li><strong>Healthcare Professionals</strong> — Doctors, nurses, and allied health professionals seeking clinical insights</li>
				<li><strong>Operations Teams</strong> — Administrators and managers optimizing hospital workflows</li>
				<li><strong>Patients & Caregivers</strong> — People seeking reliable, medically-reviewed health information</li>
				<li><strong>Health Tech Professionals</strong> — Innovators building the future of healthcare technology</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Editorial Standards</h2>
			<p>
				Every article on HealthPulse is written or reviewed by healthcare professionals with relevant domain expertise. Patient-facing health content undergoes medical review before publication. Read our full <a href="/editorial-standards/">editorial standards</a>.
			</p>

			<h2>Medical Disclaimer</h2>
			<p>
				The information on HealthPulse is for educational and informational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always consult your healthcare provider for medical decisions.
			</p>

			<h2>A MedBrains Initiative</h2>
			<p>
				HealthPulse is created by the team behind <a href="https://medbrains.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MedBrains</a> — a comprehensive Hospital Management System covering 67+ modules for Indian hospitals. Our deep understanding of hospital operations informs our editorial perspective.
			</p>

			<h2>Contact</h2>
			<p>
				Have a story tip, feedback, or want to contribute? Reach out at
				<a href="mailto:hello@healthpulse.medbrains.in">hello@healthpulse.medbrains.in</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
